Example for how to export an agent to a zip file via a command line: curl \ 'https://dialogflow.googleapis.com/v2/projects//agent:export'\ -X POST \ -H 'Authorization: Bearer '$(gcloud auth print-access-token) \ -H 'Accept: application/json' \ -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \ --compressed \ --data-binary '{}' \ | grep agentContent | sed -e 's/."agentContent": "([^"])".*/\1/' \ | base64 --decode >
